OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA chance of
OL,6,Fa few light showers affecting some
OL,7,Fcoastal districts this evening. Any
OL,8,Fshowers soon fading to leave a dry
OL,9,Fnight with some lengthy clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. A cooler night for many,
OL,11,Fcompared to recent nights. Breezy on
OL,12,Fcoasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FDry with patchy cloud,
OL,15,Fespecially through the morning, but
OL,16,Falso sunny spells which will become
OL,17,Fprolonged later. Highest temperatures
OL,18,Finland, breezy and rather cool along
OL,19,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
