OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and often cloudy, but also
OL,7,Fsome sunny spells will occur. Staying
OL,8,Fpredominantly dry, but with a small
OL,9,Fchance of coastal showers Monday.
OL,10,FTemperatures generally average or
OL,11,Fslightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
